Global Nuts and Seeds Dietary Fibers Market Insights
Nuts and Seeds Dietary Fibers Market size was valued at USD 1.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 2.8 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 8.2% from 2024 to 2030.

Nuts and Seeds Dietary Fibers Market Overview
The global nuts and seeds dietary fibers market is valued at USD 7.3 billion in 2024 and is projected to grow at a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 6.2% from 2024 to 2032. This growth is driven by the increasing consumer demand for healthy, plant-based food products rich in fiber. Additionally, the rising awareness regarding the health benefits of dietary fiber, including digestive health, weight management, and heart disease prevention, is pushing the demand for nuts and seeds as key ingredients in health-conscious diets. North America and Europe are the major markets, contributing significantly to the growth.

